<section id="customer-story" class="gray-bg centered">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2 col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 centered">
        <p class="section-title">TESTIMONIALS</p>
        <h2 class="section-heading">What our clients say about us</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="clearfix"></div>
      <div class="customer-box-wrapper centered margin-bot-35">
        <ul class="customer-logos">
          <li>
            <div class="vertical-center-wrapper">
              <div class="vertical-center-table">
                <div class="vertical-center-content">
                  <%= image_tag 'makeawish.png', class: 'customer-logo', data: {sr: 'scale up 30%'} %>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="customer-quote smallq">
              <small>In speaking to all the member of the committee including the Miami Intercontinental Hotel it was a unanimous decision. They LOVE Stilt Media!</small>
              <span class="customer-link all-caps"><a href="#0">Make a Wish</a></span>
            </div>
          </li>

          <li class="center-customer-logo">
            <div class="vertical-center-wrapper">
              <div class="vertical-center-table">
                <div class="vertical-center-content">
                  <%= image_tag 'outer.png', class: 'customer-logo', data: {sr: 'scale up 30% wait .2s'} %>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="customer-quote">
              <small>The personnel at Stilt are extremely professional and brought a lot of fresh ideas and perspectives to the table. They value both time and money and delivered the required services within the stipulated deadlines. Outer Reef Yachts will continue to do business with Stilt as projects arise. I am extremely satisfied with the way they conduct their business and hope that you have the same pleasant experience with them.</small>
              <span class="customer-link all-caps"><a href="#0">Outer Reef Yacths</a></span>
            </div>
          </li>

          <li>
            <div class="vertical-center-wrapper">
              <div class="vertical-center-table">
                <div class="vertical-center-content">
                  <%= image_tag 'bank-of-america.png', class: 'customer-logo', data: {sr: 'scale up 30% wait .4s'} %>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="customer-quote smallq">
              <small>The guys at Stilt Media are great at what they do. They really understand how to connect with our audience.</small>
              <span class="customer-link all-caps"><a href="#0">Bank of America</a></span>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="clearfix"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
